&lt;p&gt;src/org/apache/felix/dm/itest/api/FELIX5243_ConfigUpdateMissedIfComponentIsRestartingTest.java&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15258925" author="pderop" created="Tue, 26 Apr 2016 21:10:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed a patch in rv 1741103.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To avoid the race conditions, the updated method is scheduled in the component executor queue, but of course, the completion of the method is awaited from the CM thread, in case the component &quot;updated&quot; callback has thrown a configuration exception.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
